WHO   — Egwene al'Vere — the Amyrlin Seat, the Flame of Tar Valon
WHAT  — a Two Rivers innkeeper's daughter who rises to become the youngest Amyrlin Seat in history.
WHERE — WOT · The Wheel of Time  Framework inputs: the White Tower  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
